<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>voltex</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
      background: #1b1b1b;
      color: #e8e8e8;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .panel {
      background: #0d0d0f;
      border: 1px solid #2e2e32;
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 22px;
      margin: 1rem 0;
      max-width: 600px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      padding: 12px 18px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: #d1d1d1;
      color: #0a0a0a;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .btn:hover { background: #f0f0f0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>voltex</h1>

  <div class="panel">
    <h2>About Voltex</h2>
    <p>Voltex is a clean, minimal hub with a focus on speed and simplicity. This dark–grey theme keeps things lightweight while looking sharp.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="panel">
    <h2>Our Scripts</h2>
    <p>Explore our collection. The page is coming soon.</p>
    <a href="/scripts.html" class="btn">Open</a>
  </div>

  <footer style="margin-top:2rem;opacity:0.6;font-size:14px;">
    © <span id="year"></span> Voltex
  </footer>

  <script>
    document.getElementById('year').textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
  </script>

  <!-- Analytics (replace domain/ID with yours) -->
  <script defer data-domain="yourdomain.com" src="https://plausible.io/js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
